'''[[Sool]]''' waa gobol ku yaala wadanka [[Somalia]]. 
Sool, waxa ku muransan dhowr jeerna dagaalo ku dhexmareen maamulada Puntland iyo Somaliland.
Caasimadeeda gobolka  waa [[Laascaanood]] .

==Taariikh ==
Gobolkaan waxay xarun u ahayd Suldanada Daraawiishta oo boqor ka ahaa [[Diiriye Guure]] oo ka soo horjeeday gumeestayaashii dalka.

== Degmooyinka ==
Gobolka Sool wuxuu ka kooban yahay 4 degmo<ref name="Srg">{{cite web|title=Sool Region|url=http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/121024_Administrative_Map_Sool_A4.pdf|accessdate=30 December 2013}}</ref>
* [[Laascaanood]] waa caasimada Sool 
* [[Caynaba]] waxay dhanka waqooyi kagtaa laascaanood
* [[Xudun (degmo)|Xudun]]. Waa magalada 3aad ee ugu weyn gobolka marka laga yimado lascaano iyo Fardhidin waxay koonfur ka xigtaa Qawlo
* [[Taleex]]

==Muran dhul==
Intii ay jirtay dowladdii [[Siyaad Barre]] , Sool ma ahayn gobol gaar ah laakiin waxay ka mid ahayd gobolkii weynaa ee [[Nugaal]] , caasimadeeduna waxay eheed [[Garoowe]] . Waxay ka go'day Nugaal 1980-yadii, iyadoo caasimaddeeda cusub noqotay Laascaanood .<ref name=SOMALIA-1988>{{cite web
|title=Somalia (1988)
|url=http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/africa/somalia.jpg
|date=December 1988
|publisher=[[CIA]]
|accessdate=21 February 2007 }}</ref> Laga bilaabo 2003 ilaa Oktoobar 2007, Sool waxaa maamuli jiray [[Puntland]] , oo ah dhul leh qaab beeleed la mid ah. <ref name="Sqfirhbmsscf">{{Cite web |ciwaan=Somalilandâ€™s Quest for International Recognition and the HBM-SSC Factor |url=http://wardheernews.com/Articles_2010/June/Buh/29_Somaliland_recognition_%26_the_HBM-SSC_Factor.html |access-date=2021-08-09 |archive-date=2012-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120528122058/http://wardheernews.com/Articles_2010/June/Buh/29_Somaliland_recognition_%26_the_HBM-SSC_Factor.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref> sanadkii 2007, xoogag ka socda [[Somaliland]] ayaa la wareegay gacan ku haynta gobolka.

Dabayaaqadii labaatanaadkii, HBM-SSC (Hoggaanka Badbaadada iyo Mideynta SSC), oo ah urur maxalli ah oo mucaarad ah oo hadafkoodu yahay inay dhisaan maamul goboleed u gaara (Sool, Sanaag iyo Cayn ama SSC) ayaa soo baxay. <ref name="Sqfirhbmsscf"/> Kooxdu waxay la gashay wadahadalo ay la gasho dawlada Somaliland taas oo keentay inay ka qayb galaan geedi socodka siyaasada, wadahadaladaas ka dib SSC waxaa lagu soo daray dawlada hada jirta ee Somaliland.<ref>{{cite web|title=Somaliland.org|url=http://www.somaliland.org/2012/10/22/somaliland-xagla-toosiye-oo-xilkii-kula-wareegay-xafladii-ugu-balaadhnayd-ee-wasiir-xil-ku-tirsado/|accessdate=26 February 2017|ciwaan=Nuqul Archive|archive-date=27 February 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170227231729/http://www.somaliland.org/2012/10/22/somaliland-xagla-toosiye-oo-xilkii-kula-wareegay-xafladii-ugu-balaadhnayd-ee-wasiir-xil-ku-tirsado/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>


